{"tid":1301284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飲還飲，寶礦力膠樽要回收！","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T02:05:58.000Z","uid":36073,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1a20591d9096a04ff48dc0f56ed7c2c27a9411","tid":1301284,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"因為寶礦力撤回廣告，所以你買寶礦力<br />\n因為你愛香港嘅美麗，所以要回收 <img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QHk0PNp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHk0PNp.gif&h=b74cbab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">飲完唔好就咁丟落垃圾筒呀，沖乾淨放入回收箱更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你怕樓下個回收箱根本係等同送入堆填區，<br />\n有心有力嘅就直接帶去「綠在區區」回收站或者民間自發「不是垃圾站」啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「綠在區區」地址：<a href=\"https://www.wastereduction.gov.hk/tc/community/cgs_intro.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wastereduction.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommunity%2Fcgs_intro.htm&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=86a88721\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wastereduction.gov.hk/tc/community/cgs_intro.htm</a><br />\n「不是垃圾站」：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WasteNoMall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWasteNoMall%2F&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=e84d5204\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WasteNoMall/</a>"},{"pid":"214a17a5812e0e679407fc4174c5cf30e2a5b210","tid":1301284,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a71cec994745082d6b15d3032fc43ac2a4a3b510","tid":1301284,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"愛香港嘅你，要回收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi